                    <h4>ISO 29990:2010: Learning Services for Non-Formal Education and Training Certification</h4>
                    
                    <p>
                        ISO 29990 is a quality management system standard for providers of education and training services. ISO 29990 gives a unified model for a quality and professional mode of operation, as well as a ordinary reference point for both LSPs and their clients for the conceptualization, development and delivery of the particular program.


                    </p>
                    <p>
