                    </p>
                    <p>
                        ISO 29990 is essentially subdivided into two areas: learning services (for example, these services include designing, given that and monitoring of learning services) and management at the learning service supplier for example business planning, financial management, risk management as well as human resources management. This Standard is the first Standard for learning providers that is applicable and applied on an international scale. The advantages for learning providers are transparency of their own services, global comparability and defined procedures for quality assurance. Mapple Certification is an objective demonstration of conformity, creating confidence for learners and other concerned parties in the capacity of the organization to achieve quality throughout the learning procedure.

